{
  "message": "Improve mobile accessibility for Hero and PromptCard components\n\nHero.tsx:\n- Replace Badge components with proper <button> elements\n- Add aria-pressed state for category filter buttons\n- Add role=\"group\" with aria-label for filter container\n- Increase touch target to 44px minimum (min-h-[44px])\n- Add touch-manipulation for better mobile response\n\nPromptCard.tsx:\n- Increase button touch targets to 44px on mobile (h-11)\n- Add aria-label to Copy, Add to basket, and View buttons\n- Add touch-manipulation CSS property\n- Responsive button labels (icons only on mobile, with text on larger screens)\n\nThese changes follow WCAG 2.1 guidelines for touch target size (44px)\nand proper ARIA semantics for toggle buttons.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
